\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"飲落喉嚨更加唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd36ce1d7cd1d0d972bb8b14e92865575741b4a","tid":1970411,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b2c06f24ace0cc083450f49098e06d547f5ad75","tid":1970411,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9fa3374d72b881e40fb4bd0d125c100f889f8be","tid":1970411,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"小心d雲耳有毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"吃了兩舊唔吃了，酸中帶藥味，我頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"根據《華商報》報道，進食木耳後中毒的事件不止一次。 2016年遼寧有對夫婦，進食浸泡約2天的黑木耳後，肝腎衰竭，中毒休克。 2015年長沙有位女士吃了浸泡2天的木耳後，因多個器官衰竭而身亡；浙江有位男士吃了浸泡3天的黑木耳，也引發器官衰竭，搶救一星期才脫險。<br />\n浙江近日有女童進食涼拌黑木耳後食物中毒，性命垂危；安徽上月有5歲男童進食木耳炒雞蛋後，肚痛及口吐白沫，送院後不治。<br />\n若進食後中毒，患者會出現急性肝、腎功能衰竭，表癥為：極度疲倦乏力，胃口欠佳、嘔吐和腹脹等。若為神經毒性，可能出現血液、肌肉溶解症狀。<br />\n<br />\n鬼國好多人食雲耳食到無命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b473b7ca4a1401ecbc193711f70d8ab0da928271","tid":1970411,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"errrrr..."},{"pid":"ee2a2256928d741223260b7b386b95d8278bf35f","tid":1970411,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73fb5b25727ca30a2b5a0829641ed08160eb3ac","tid":1970411,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10aa14c09cc1a16c3696321b40d0b028e34086fd","tid":1970411,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"啲飯好似發水咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"弘，總之成個餐啲野都唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T0